-- MOVES-Robert Lyon rejoins CI Investments 
-- 
-- Mon Oct 06, 2014 02:47PM EDT
-- None



Oct 6 (Reuters) - Canadian investment company CI Investments Inc named Robert Lyon senior vice-president, portfolio management to its Signature Global Asset Management team, effective before Jan. 1, 2015.

Lyon will be responsible for Signature's resource-focused funds and foreign and domestic natural resource equity holdings within other Signature funds, CI said. He will also be named lead portfolio manager of Signature Global Resource Fund, Signature Global Resource Corporate Class, Signature Global Energy Corporate Class and Signature Gold Corporate Class.